        <briefdescription>
<para>Set the options for the interrupt controller driver. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>In Cascade mode same Option is set to Slave controllers.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the <ref refid="struct_x_intc" kindref="compound">XIntc</ref> instance to be worked on. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Options</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>to be set. The available options are described in <ref refid="xintc_8h" kindref="compound">xintc.h</ref>.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if the options were set successfully</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_INVALID_PARAM if the specified option was not valid</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>None. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
